---
// SocialProofVideo.astro
---
<section class="py-24 bg-brand-dark border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    
    <!-- Video Wrapper -->
    <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-video bg-black shadow-2xl border border-white/10 group cursor-pointer">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand-dark/40 group-hover:bg-brand-dark/20 transition-colors z-10 flex items-center justify-center">
        <!-- Play Button -->
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-brand-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center pl-2 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,184,0,0.6)] transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
           <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-dark" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM9.555 7.168A1 1 0 008 8v4a1 1 0 001.555.832l3-2a1 1 0 000-1.664l-3-2z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Placeholder image for video thumbnail -->
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573164713988-8665fc963095?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Mensagem do CEO" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60" />
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial Content -->
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">Um número para comemorar com os +10.000 Afiliados</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text/80 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        "Nossa missão nos últimos 2 anos foi dar justiça e poder ao afiliado. Quando você começa a ver o retorno sobre investimento (ROI) verdadeiro porque a Ratoeira está barrando os robôs... O jogo muda."
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white/10 rounded-full overflow-hidden border border-brand-yellow/30">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560250097-0b93528c311a?auto=format&fit=crop&w=150&q=80" alt="CEO" class="w-full h-full object-cover mix-blend-luminosity hover:mix-blend-normal transition-all" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Nome do CEO</h4>
          <span class="text-xs text-brand-yellow uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">Founder, Ratoeira Ads</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
